==Icelandic==

===Noun===

'''strætó''' ''m.''

# (city) [[bus]], [[omnibus]]
: [[ég]] ætla bara að [[taka]] '''strætó'''
: ''[[I'm]] just going to [[take]] '''the bus'''''
: [[hvenær]] [[koma|kemur]] strætóinn?
: ''[[when]] does the bus arrive?''

==Idioms==

*að taka strætó
:to take the bus

